  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the Territorialization of the Public Policy of Attention, Assistance and Comprehensive Reparation to the Victims of the Internal Armed Conflict, in the Framework of the NDP 2018-2022</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project contributes to the creation of mechanisms of articulation between the public policy of victims in Colombia. In particular, it aims at implement preventive measures, protection, care, assistance and comprehensive reparation to ensure the effective enjoyment of rights. The project also focuses on the stabilization planning instruments based on the development of the institutional capacities of the departments and municipalities, as well as the support of the implementation of human rights actions developed by the government. The proposed activities seek to strengthen information systems, contribute to the qualification of the knowledge of servants and public officials, as well as strengthening institutional response capacities from the execution of projects, among others.</narrative>
  </description>
